{"tid":710203,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"山寨新垣結衣進軍日本發片　歌聲被網友譏笑：像在唱兒歌","createTime":"2018-06-20T14:19:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-21T07:44:15.000Z","uid":9573,"like":1,"dislike":65,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"a7c24a3149e5cbc6ad0d23b58fb37e4dfb0747b5","tid":710203,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T14:19:56.000Z","msg":"大陸女模龍夢柔因長相酷似新垣結衣紅到日本，被製作人相中受邀客串日劇《愛情重跑》，今（20）她公開翻唱神曲《PLANET》中、日文版本的MV連結，宣告正式出道，歌聲卻被網友虧笑：「好像在唱兒歌！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2018/06/20/1409972-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2018%2F06%2F20%2F1409972-XXL.jpg&h=20ea9db0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▲龍夢柔（左）長相酷似新垣結衣爆紅。<br />\n<br />\n龍夢柔去年底因IG照片被日本網友廣傳爆紅，成為當地媒體爭相報導的對象，她開始參演各大綜藝節目，甚至客串日劇《愛情重跑》以雙語演出。今天她在個人IG貼出宣傳照，公告自己翻唱已經解散的樂團「Lambsey」的神曲《PLANET》，並貼上中、日兩版的MV連結，引發網友熱烈討論。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2018/06/20/1409970-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2018%2F06%2F20%2F1409970-XXL.jpg&h=ccd1032f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▲龍夢柔進軍日本發行單曲。<br />\n<br />\n事實上，龍夢柔19日已在上海搶先曝光新歌，她與歌曲原創人井上慎二郎一起登台，吸引千名粉絲到場支持，下半場大迫勇也接應角球，升至最高點一頂，皮球飛向遠柱中內柱入網。不過她從素人變身成歌手出道，似乎沒有接受太多歌唱訓練，被網友痛批「真的很難聽」、「好像在唱兒歌」、「一開口我就關掉了」、「修音的地方也太明顯了」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/qzyL9SJ30do\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FqzyL9SJ30do&d=gVBwHMV%2BUKRpFY4WJToIjTCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=058e657c\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/qzyL9SJ30do</a><br />\n<br />\n加上龍夢柔曾在爆紅後接受媒體採訪，透露自己拒絕許多大公司，「我沒有明星夢，我終究不是新垣結衣，我就是一個普通大學生」，如今不只出道發片，還放話要在日本、大陸兩地展開演藝活動，讓網友全看傻眼。"},{"pid":"34424b27c6caf14916e2def2e74adea5778da6a5","tid":710203,"uid":94828,"like":41,"dislike":0,"score":41,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T14:20:50.000Z","msg":"好撚樣衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f17eb13a6767ef22030e71b961498612b3f7b15","tid":710203,"uid":55405,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T14:53:08.000Z","msg":"屌佢收得皮未 一日到黑用結衣個名 比佢影衰曬囉 chok住角度影佢攰唔攰 完全無忽似囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7835d5528acbf64050ffaa7edde3b47303d597bc","tid":710203,"uid":3794,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T15:22:54.000Z","msg":"若巴點睇千雪bb上咗美女廚房"},{"pid":"c128af97c248c38fff0978f7a74057d2121efa62","tid":710203,"uid":153497,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T01:26:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">下半場大迫勇也接應角球，升至最高點一頂，皮球飛向遠柱中內柱入網。</span></span>"},{"pid":"6331601946fc4fd3df94c3b8e38357cc7e983753","tid":710203,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T01:27:57.000Z","msg":"嗯"},{"pid":"26fd627e6db910a88beeb64286d9d3fbf7e87c78","tid":710203,"uid":37524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T01:33:44.000Z","msg":"登台係咪開恥笑大會?"},{"pid":"c36cc112eafede9e8ee4f1cb8614b883f913dacc","tid":710203,"uid":52595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T01:38:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"59ac8e95697f3ed7f9017bafb857032eccda4791","tid":710203,"uid":65074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T01:45:01.000Z","msg":"化行妝抄足都有浸村姑味"},{"pid":"98fcc06a87fe03c624b8b62b57412807223707ad","tid":710203,"uid":25560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T01:46:12.000Z","msg":"垃圾番版"},{"pid":"4623356575f6298f63401f1f16b9e9a72bcc4790","tid":710203,"uid":123738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T01:47:07.000Z","msg":"支那雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d6ff56aa72a4ec86e7850d916901c4d66389e02","tid":710203,"uid":15,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T01:50:22.000Z","msg":"垃圾